{"id":230817,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/google提议为审查设立专门的http状态码/","date":"2012-06-12T14:53:11Z","modified":"2012-06-12T17:30:29Z","title":"Google提议为审查设立专门的HTTP状态码","content":"<p>XML合作者、Google Android开发大使Tim Bray递交了新的HTTP状态码草案，应用于因法律限制而无法显示的网页。新的状态码为“451 Unavailable for Legal Reasons”，访问者将会知道他们请求的网页或资源是因为国家审查的原因而无法访问。根据451草案，使用451代码应需要指明相关的法律限制细节，以及背后的执法机构和限制针对是哪类资源。在此之前，英国ISP遵循法庭命令屏蔽海盗湾时使用的是“403 Forbidden”，有博客指出403状态码代表的是“服务器拒绝履行请求”，但实际上海盗湾服务器根本没收到请求，因而403状态码是不合适的。根据Bray的提议，使用451状态码是可选的。<img src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/2044f08e/mf.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/viral/sendEmail.cfm?lang=en&amp;title=Google%E6%8F%90%E8%AE%AE%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E8%AE%BE%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84HTTP%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%A0%81&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F06%2F12%2F1112215%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Google%E6%8F%90%E8%AE%AE%E4%B8%BA%E5%AE%A1%E6%9F%A5%E8%AE%BE%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%93%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84HTTP%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%A0%81&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D12%2F06%2F12%2F1112215%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/136716336169/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2044f08e/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/136716336169/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2044f08e/a2.img\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a><img src=\"http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/136716336169/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/2044f08e/a2t.img\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<di